data.description: The view is wonderful and so much to offer in this open concept, adorable home on 1.22 acres. Privacy with convenience, you can't ask for more! This home was renovated in 2021 with new roof, siding, windows, appliances, island, counter tops of granite, bathrooms, doors and a high efficiency multi-zone heat pump and a hot water heater!!! On the lower level,  a wet bar with a mini fridge, primary bedroom, living area and a walk out. Perfect for an in law suite, guests, rental or just more room for entertaining!                                                          ****BACK ON MARKET BECAUSE BUYERS FINANCING FELL THROUGH****                                                                                ***SELLERS are giving a BONUS of snow removal for the entire first year to BUYERS . It will be added to the contract.
